    <section id="projects">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="project">
            <h3>Netflix clone </h3>
            <p>The Netflix clone project was a personal endeavor aimed at replicating the user interface and experience of the popular streaming platform, Netflix. Leveraging HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this project focused on creating a basic yet functional representation of Netflix's front-end.</p>
            <h3>Weather application</h3>
            <p>The Weather App project was a dynamic web-based application aimed at providing real-time weather information to users based on their location or a specific city. Leveraging HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, along with an API from OpenWeatherMap, this project offered a user-friendly interface for accessing weather forecasts.</p>
